                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FR-7</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Code search (developers/admins can search .pm and .tt files)</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">🟠 High</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Special queries</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FR-8</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Real-time doc index updates when .tt files change</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">🟠 High</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Backend only</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FR-9</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Conversation resume page at /ai/conversations with search, filter, and context preservation</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">🟠 High</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Yes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FR-10</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Chat widget UI design matching Grok.ai aesthetic (dark theme, modern typography, responsive)</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">🟠 High</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Yes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FR-11</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Admin controls to change model and agent assignments without code changes (dynamic config)</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">🟠 High</td>
                        <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Admin only</td>
                    </tr>
