                                • 🆕 Conversation resume functionality with full context preservation<br>
                                • Inject on all pages
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">4: Admin & Verification</td>
                            <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">2-3 weeks</td>
