                                • 🆕 Agent configuration UI (enable/disable agents, set default models per agent)<br>
                                • 🆕 Grok API key management with encryption<br>
                                • Web search approval workflow<br>
                                • Analytics dashboard<br>
                                • Database UI integration<br>
                                • API key management (Kubernetes-ready)
